      "description": "Per the device submission plan and ASME V&V 40 Section 6.4, validation of the hemolysis prediction model shall be supported by a controlled experiment in which independent variables (flow rate, rotational speed) are systematically manipulated under pre-specified conditions, with appropriate controls, to isolate model prediction error from confounding sources. A controlled-experiment design is required to ensure that the validation dataset provides sufficient internal validity for regulatory submission at Model Risk Level 2.",
